         We’d love to see you there!
        </AuHeading>
        <AuContent>
          <p>Our guides are thrilled to help you out on our Discord Channel.</p>
        </AuContent>

        <p class="au-c-para au-u-margin-top">
          <AuLink href="https://discord.gg/eScePvyv" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="au-c-button au-c-button--large au-u-margin-bottom">
            <AuIcon @icon="arrow-right" @size="large" @alignment="left" /> Join the Discord channel
          </AuLink>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="au-o-grid__item au-u-3-4">
        <img src="/images/discord.png">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

